106
00:08:34,380 --> 00:08:34,830
Hello.

107
00:08:35,210 --> 00:08:36,130
What? Did you catch him?

108
00:08:36,150 --> 00:08:37,309
Okay, I'll be right there.

109
00:08:39,870 --> 00:08:41,140
Go. Come with me.

110
00:08:41,220 --> 00:08:41,620
