I dreamed that

118
00:09:10,970 --> 00:09:11,770
I caught Wang Zhishui.

119
00:09:12,140 --> 00:09:12,700
Then?

120
00:09:13,880 --> 00:09:14,520
Then.

121
00:09:14,630 --> 00:09:16,160
