122
00:09:17,470 --> 00:09:19,870
I chopped off his fingers one by one.

123
00:09:21,890 --> 00:09:23,600
That's vicious.

124
00:09:25,780 --> 00:09:26,200
All right.

125
00:09:26,960 --> 00:09:28,070
I'm hanging up.

126
00:09:28,600 --> 00:09:29,320
I'm still working.

127
00:09:30,540 --> 00:09:31,260
Okay, bye bye.

128
00:09:31,470 --> 00:09:32,240
Sure, bye.

129
00:09:42,190 --> 00:09:43,270
