141
00:10:00,310 --> 00:10:00,990
How was he caught?

142
00:10:01,310 --> 00:10:02,190
Come on. Let me tell you.

143
00:10:02,360 --> 00:10:03,480
This thief is really odd.

144
00:10:03,670 --> 00:10:05,230
He never took the liquor with him after his theft.

145
00:10:05,260 --> 00:10:06,190
He finished the liquor on the spot.

146
00:10:06,330 --> 00:10:07,380
Guess what happened this time.

147
00:10:07,870 --> 00:10:08,470
What?

148
00:10:08,550 --> 00:10:09,980
He got drunk and slept through the night until morning.

149
00:10:10,060 --> 00:10:11,110
He even didn't get awake the next day.

150
00:10:11,130 --> 00:10:12,000
And my uncle came back.

151
00:10:14,980 --> 00:10:15,380
He...

152
00:10:15,500 --> 00:10:17,290
He is so odd.

153
00:10:17,820 --> 00:10:18,460
What's his name?

154
00:10:19,340 --> 00:10:20,770
It seems to be Li Zhishui?

155
00:10:21,510 --> 00:10:24,110
Probably Wang Zhishui?

156
00:10:24,470 --> 00:10:25,610
I don't remember anyway.

157
00:10:26,050 --> 00:10:27,290
I can only remember the last name.

158
00:10:27,320 --> 00:10:28,280
"The Myth of Dayu and the Great Flood," right?

159
00:10:30,480 --> 00:10:31,200
Where is he right now?

160
00:10:31,890 --> 00:10:32,920
He's at my uncle's house.

161
00:10:32,960 --> 00:10:34,330
We made a police report just now and don't now whether he has been arrested.

162
00:10:35,420 --> 00:10:36,270
Take me there right away.

163
00:10:36,340 --> 00:10:36,890
Go.

164
00:10:36,910 --> 00:10:37,340
But...

165
00:10:37,380 --> 00:10:38,110
You...

166
00:10:38,150 --> 00:10:39,190
Do you know him?

167
00:10:39,220 --> 00:10:40,100
Stop asking me.

168
00:10:40,340 --> 00:10:41,260
Just take me there.

169
00:10:41,810 --> 00:10:42,120
Go.

170
00:10:42,640 --> 00:10:43,250
Go.

171
00:10:53,170 --> 00:10:53,810
Do you want

172
00:10:54,230 --> 00:10:55,920
