173
00:10:56,260 --> 00:10:57,070
What do you mean?

174
00:10:58,340 --> 00:10:59,630
Tell you good news.

175
00:11:00,290 --> 00:11:01,170
I might have caught

176
00:11:01,310 --> 00:11:02,020
Wang Zhishui.

177
00:11:03,920 --> 00:11:04,960
This guy has the same name.

178
00:11:05,370 --> 00:11:06,870
He might be the one you're looking for.

179
00:11:10,030 --> 00:11:10,410
Okay.

180
00:11:10,760 --> 00:11:11,800
I'll send you the address.

181
00:11:25,660 --> 00:11:26,410
Where is he?

182
00:11:31,260 --> 00:11:31,840
Here.

183
00:11:34,310 --> 00:11:35,130
Are the police inside?

184
00:11:35,220 --> 00:11:36,730
Yeah, they locked him inside.

185
00:11:48,380 --> 00:11:48,890
Where is he?

186
00:11:51,210 --> 00:11:51,830
Locked inside.

187
00:11:54,170 --> 00:11:54,960
You can't go in.

188
00:11:55,920 --> 00:11:57,440
I'll kill this guy today.

189
00:11:57,830 --> 00:11:59,170
The police are interrogating him in there.

190
00:12:02,870 --> 00:12:03,460
Besides,

191
00:12:04,120 --> 00:12:05,050
you haven't even seen his face.

192
00:12:05,710 --> 00:12:07,090
You are not sure he's the right guy.

193
00:12:08,300 --> 00:12:10,070
There aren't that many thieves called Wang Zhishui.

194
00:12:19,190 --> 00:12:20,110
He's the one.

195
00:12:20,820 --> 00:12:21,940
I would recognize him even if he has turned into ashes.

196
00:12:22,980 --> 00:12:23,690
Be quiet.

197
00:12:24,610 --> 00:12:25,980
Talk to the police later if you have something to report.

198
00:12:26,610 --> 00:12:27,450
Stop making noise.

199
00:12:27,470 --> 00:12:28,210
Hebei, Langfang.

200
00:12:29,280 --> 00:12:31,060
- Isn't he from Shandong?
- Hebei, Langfang?

201
00:12:31,990 --> 00:12:33,070
That's near here.

202
00:12:35,560 --> 00:12:37,770
I can head home once a month.

203
00:12:39,870 --> 00:12:40,990
Isn't he an orphan?

204
00:12:42,590 --> 00:12:45,070
He really cheated the hell out of you.

205
00:12:48,530 --> 00:12:49,730
Take him back to the station for now.

206
00:12:51,900 --> 00:12:52,840
Don't worry.

207
00:12:58,940 --> 00:13:00,130
Do you know how much I hate him?

208
00:13:00,890 --> 00:13:02,360
The clothes I wore when I carried him,

209
00:13:02,820 --> 00:13:03,850
and the sheets and sofa cover

210
00:13:04,150 --> 00:13:04,990
he slept on.

211
00:13:06,090 --> 00:13:06,890
