212
00:13:08,520 --> 00:13:09,100
Enough.

213
00:13:09,980 --> 00:13:10,750
Say something serious.

214
00:13:11,820 --> 00:13:13,040
He stole from you twice.

215
00:13:13,570 --> 00:13:15,230
Did he leave any evidence behind?

216
00:13:16,740 --> 00:13:17,530
Well, he did.

217
00:13:20,480 --> 00:13:21,660
I just told you. I burned everything.

218
00:13:22,300 --> 00:13:23,280
I burned everything.

219
00:13:26,050 --> 00:13:27,560
I told you to put on records but you didn't.

220
00:13:28,080 --> 00:13:29,050
If you did,

221
00:13:29,660 --> 00:13:31,390
you could have handed everything over for the investigations.

222
00:13:32,380 --> 00:13:34,090
You lost tens of thousands.

223
00:13:34,970 --> 00:13:35,930
That's enough to keep him in jail for a few years.

224
00:13:36,580 --> 00:13:37,700
Right now, he only stole three bottles of liquor.

225
00:13:38,500 --> 00:13:40,020
Those cost less than Â¥2,000 in total.

226
00:13:40,660 --> 00:13:41,890
That amount is not enough to get him sentenced.

227
00:13:42,290 --> 00:13:43,690
At most, he'll be locked up in the detention cell for 15 days.

228
00:13:45,650 --> 00:13:47,140
I don't want him in jail for years.

229
00:13:48,110 --> 00:13:49,420
I don't want to get my items back either.

230
00:13:50,110 --> 00:13:51,150
I just want to catch him.

231
00:13:53,440 --> 00:13:55,070
If he is really locked up for a couple of years,

232
00:13:55,850 --> 00:13:57,220
how long will I have to wait for him to be released?

233
00:13:59,170 --> 00:14:00,030
Fine, whatever.

234
00:14:49,930 --> 00:14:51,330
It's so late. Why don't you come back?

235
00:14:51,980 --> 00:14:53,240
My work is piling up.

236
00:14:53,450 --> 00:14:54,630
I plan to sleep in the office.

237
00:14:54,790 --> 00:14:56,140
You leave Yuan Ru at home alone?

238
00:14:56,140 --> 00:14:56,610
No.

239
00:14:56,990 --> 00:14:57,920
She's traveling abroad.

240
00:14:58,260 --> 00:14:58,800
That's perfect.

241
00:14:59,550 --> 00:15:00,460
I just finished my work.

242
00:15:00,790 --> 00:15:02,480
My mom might wake up if I return so late.

243
00:15:03,110 --> 00:15:04,460
Let me crash here for the night.

244
00:15:08,330 --> 00:15:09,300
Don't take advantage of this.

245
00:15:24,540 --> 00:15:25,940
What's the point of playing that game all day long?

246
00:15:27,560 --> 00:15:28,520
Idiot.

247
00:15:30,170 --> 00:15:31,050
When I was in the army,

248
00:15:31,430 --> 00:15:32,940
electronic devices were prohibited.

249
00:15:33,810 --> 00:15:34,920
Especially for snipers like me,

250
00:15:35,320 --> 00:15:36,440
it is important to protect eyesight.

251
00:15:38,060 --> 00:15:39,780
It has been years since you left the army.

252
00:15:41,500 --> 00:15:43,480
I don't see you have kept up with the times.

253
00:15:46,650 --> 00:15:47,970
A mobile phone like yours

254
00:15:48,830 --> 00:15:50,340
can't even use WeChat.

255
00:15:56,680 --> 00:15:57,350
Anyway,

256
00:15:57,710 --> 00:15:59,160
why haven't I seen your sister recently?

257
00:16:01,050 --> 00:16:01,780
Didn't I tell you?

258
00:16:02,020 --> 00:16:02,890
She's traveling abroad.

259
00:16:03,950 --> 00:16:05,790
But even during my training here,

260
00:16:05,830 --> 00:16:06,830
I rarely saw her.

261
00:16:09,680 --> 00:16:10,160
What's that matter?

262
00:16:11,470 --> 00:16:12,200
Do you miss her?

263
00:16:17,500 --> 00:16:18,470
