266
00:16:24,500 --> 00:16:25,760
Isn't your sister your entire world?

267
00:16:26,870 --> 00:16:28,260
Why would you spare a thought for me?

268
00:16:29,920 --> 00:16:31,020
I don't.

269
00:16:31,330 --> 00:16:32,270
I'm considering for both of you.

270
00:16:33,330 --> 00:16:34,370
You can take a horse to water, but you can't make it drink.

271
00:16:35,070 --> 00:16:35,950
Since it is impossible,

272
00:16:36,770 --> 00:16:37,260
I might as well

273
00:16:37,760 --> 00:16:39,000
